Trinity::

She cried on her front paws. Then she lifted her head, tears still 
rolling down her cheeks, but now with a glimmer of hope. She looked 
at Archangle and Koj."You mean that they may still be alive? 
You....you really  think that...that they might have survived the 
crash?" She stood up and put her front paws on Koj's leg, looking up 
at him."Can we go and see them please? I just got to find my mom and 
dad. Oh pleeeaaasssee can we go and find them?" her tears starting to 
dry up and the wet streaks that ran from her eyes down to her fangs 
was slowly disappearing.  Her face had a look of hopefullness about 
it. "Please?"
